-- Monte Paschi Considers Viola, Valeri, Maioli for CEO, MF Reports
-- B y   A r m o r e l   K e n n a
-- 2011-12-30T09:09:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-30/monte-paschi-considers-viola-valeri-maioli-for-ceo-mf-reports.html
Banca Monte dei Paschi di Siena SpA (BMPS) 
chief executive officer candidates include Fabrizio Viola,
Flavio Valeri and Giampiero Maioli, newspaper MF reported,
without saying where it got the information.  Viola is CEO of  Banca Popolare dell’Emilia Romagna Scrl (BPE) ,
Valeri is  Deutsche Bank (DBK)  AG’s top executive in Italy, while
Maioli is CEO of  Credit Agricole SA (ACA)  unit Cariparma.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Armorel Kenna in Milan at 
 akenna@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sara Marley at 
